Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:55.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:55.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,懸命の祈り届くか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:55.29,default,,0,0,0,,Will Kaiji's prayers be answered?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:55.65,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Afterglow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.44,0:01:02.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふっふっふ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.44,0:01:02.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,二度もチャンスを
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.44,0:01:02.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,与えられては引きたくなくとも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:01:00.79,default,,0,0,0,,By giving me a second chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:03.81,default,,0,0,0,,I will draw the winning ticket,\Neven if I didn't want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.15,0:01:04.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引いてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.06,0:01:06.96,default,,0,0,0,,I was born under a lucky star,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.08,0:01:06.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしはそういう星の下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:13.03,default,,0,0,0,,and that's why I will keep\Nwinning, winning and winning...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:11.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝って勝って勝って勝って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:16.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ちまくる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:16.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういう星の下に生まれておる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:16.29,default,,0,0,0,,That is how lucky I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.74,0:01:21.49,default,,0,0,0,,Luck for a mortal like you\Nis totally different from mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.79,0:01:21.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しょせん凡人である
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.79,0:01:21.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君などとは運の要領が違う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.75,0:01:26.32,default,,0,0,0,,What is "common"\Nis different for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.90,0:01:27.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よって常識が違う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.90,0:01:27.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしのように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.32,0:01:29.86,default,,0,0,0,,I'm favoured by luck,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.30,0:01:29.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,運に寵愛されし者にとって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:33.27,default,,0,0,0,,so being 'lucky'\Nis normal for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.91,0:01:34.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,幸運はもう日常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.91,0:01:34.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実を言うなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.08,0:01:37.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１回目に引くこともできた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.26,0:01:40.01,default,,0,0,0,,With my luck, I could have drawn\Nthe winning lot during the first draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:40.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしの運をもってすればな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.18,0:01:43.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっはっは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.18,0:01:43.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかしそれでは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:46.91,default,,0,0,0,,But if that's the case, there's no\Nsatisfaction or excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.59,0:01:46.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あまりにあっさりして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.59,0:01:46.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,味気ないので
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:51.92,default,,0,0,0,,So I held back a little
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:50.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしはあえて己が強運を少し緩め
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:53.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君に一度だけチャンスを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:55.66,default,,0,0,0,,to give you\Na chance to draw, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:56.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,回してやったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:02:00.90,default,,0,0,0,,But you did not make use of\Nthat one valuable chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.07,0:01:58.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのにカイジ君は貴重な一度を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:02.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生かせなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:02.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この一度の
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.19,0:02:06.63,default,,0,0,0,,That touch of\Nbad luck is fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:06.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言うなら不運が既に致命的なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:10.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっはっはっは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:10.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残念だが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:12.90,default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately for you,\Nthere is no way you can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:13.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君にもう勝ち目はない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:16.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜならわしはこういうとき
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:15.64,default,,0,0,0,,Because at times like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:19.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういう訳か引いてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:18.88,default,,0,0,0,,I will draw the winning lot,\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:22.12,default,,0,0,0,,I don't really want to draw it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:22.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分では大して引きたくもない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:24.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当はもっと楽しみたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:26.80,default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping to enjoy this a little\Nlonger, but I'll end up drawing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:27.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引いてしまうのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:30.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうわけかな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.36,0:02:29.59,default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:31.46,default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:32.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:32.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:32.97,default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.14,0:02:42.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっはっはっは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.14,0:02:42.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では証明しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:44.24,default,,0,0,0,,Now, let me prove\Nmy words to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:44.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしの大言壮語
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:49.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よろしいか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:48.45,default,,0,0,0,,Is this fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:51.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっはっは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:51.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.89,0:02:52.08,default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.95,0:02:56.22,default,,0,0,0,,He draws!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:03:00.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,選択
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:03:00.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:03:00.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２度目の選択
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:59.85,default,,0,0,0,,The director takes his\Nsecond chance at the draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:02.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけるな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:02.44,default,,0,0,0,,This is rubbish!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.86,0:03:04.98,default,,0,0,0,,What nonsense is he\Ntalking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:05.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何を馬鹿なことを
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:05.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前のような
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:07.86,default,,0,0,0,,An evil person like you\Nwill never draw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:09.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪党が引けるものか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:09.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引けない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:11.60,default,,0,0,0,,You can't draw it!\NNo! You must not draw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:12.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:12.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引いちゃいけないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:15.60,default,,0,0,0,,If god is merciful, he should\Nlet me draw it instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:14.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神に慈悲があるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:14.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:18.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪党より俺だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:18.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺を救うべきだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:20.07,default,,0,0,0,,I should be saved! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:20.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:40.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引くな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:40.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引くんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:38.62,default,,0,0,0,,Don't draw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:41.54,default,,0,0,0,,Don't draw it!\NYou can't draw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:47.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引いちゃ駄目だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:47.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外せ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:47.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外せ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:43.35,default,,0,0,0,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:46.63,default,,0,0,0,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:51.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うーうーふふ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:54.14,default,,0,0,0,,It's a miss!\NIt's got to be a miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:54.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハズレだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:54.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハズレに決まっている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:57.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:04:00.14,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...\Na most unfortunate result!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.62,0:04:00.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とても残念な結果だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:08.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うふーふーふふ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:08.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うふーふふ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:11.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふっふっふっふっふっふっふ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:14.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うふー
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:14.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どっちだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:14.16,default,,0,0,0,,So what is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:17.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっきり言え
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:16.89,default,,0,0,0,,Be clear about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:19.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残念な結果だなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:19.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どっちにでも
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:22.17,default,,0,0,0,,An "unfortunate result"\Ncan mean many things!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:22.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,取れるような言い方しやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:27.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うーふふふふふふ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:27.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:27.17,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:31.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どっちにでも取れるはなかろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.40,0:04:30.32,default,,0,0,0,,How can it be anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:33.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしはさっき
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:33.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:35.22,default,,0,0,0,,I said that I wanted to\Nenjoy this a little longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:37.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽しみたいが多分そうはならない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:37.01,default,,0,0,0,,but I guess that is\Nnot going to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:40.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おそらく当たりを引いてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:43.01,default,,0,0,0,,I said that I would probably\Ndraw the winning ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:47.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう言ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:47.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その言葉通りに取れば良い
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:47.46,default,,0,0,0,,You just need to interpret things\Nthe way I said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:51.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.26,default,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:57.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっあああっあっあ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:04.39,default,,0,0,0,,This is what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:04.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こういうこと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:17.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:17.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:17.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:19.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:08.88,default,,0,0,0,,The winning ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:11.34,default,,0,0,0,,The winning ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:13.98,default,,0,0,0,,The winning ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:16.22,default,,0,0,0,,The winning ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:18.82,default,,0,0,0,,The winning ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:29.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐひい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:29.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ばかな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:29.10,default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:35.26,default,,0,0,0,,Why?! How did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:35.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何で
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:35.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何でこんな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:41.81,default,,0,0,0,,How can such a thing\Nactually happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:42.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなことが現実に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:46.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっあああああ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:46.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:47.05,default,,0,0,0,,H-He actually drew\Nthe winning ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:48.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引き当てた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:48.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何10分の１という
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:50.47,default,,0,0,0,,Despite the overwhelming odds\Nagainst him...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:51.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確率なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:51.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなもの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:56.52,default,,0,0,0,,He did it as if\Nit was always meant to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:54.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ものともせずに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:54.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっさりと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:59.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり前みたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:59.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:00.59,default,,0,0,0,,Such a person\Nactually exists!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:02.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな人間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:02.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,他を圧する
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:04.53,default,,0,0,0,,They possess amazing luck\Nand defeat everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:06.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対的強運の持ち主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:06.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怪物が
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:06.73,default,,0,0,0,,They're monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:10.36,default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bring some\Nbandages and gauze.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:10.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:10.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持って来なさい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:10.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,包帯やガーゼ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:13.47,default,,0,0,0,,We should be prepared to\Nat least stem the bleeding...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:15.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せめて止血の用意だけは万全に
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:14.37,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:19.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:18.78,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:21.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ううううっうっううう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:25.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっうっう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:25.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ううっう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:27.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あはー
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:34.69,default,,0,0,0,,Execution time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:34.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,執行だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:43.80,default,,0,0,0,,- He's kidding, right?\N- Is he for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:43.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うそだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:43.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本気かよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.20,default,,0,0,0,,Is he really going that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:46.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこまでやるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:49.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:49.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいカイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:56.71,default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:07:01.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,駄目だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:07:01.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,失う
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:07:01.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,失ってしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:03.20,default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to lose\Nthese fingers...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:07.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この指を
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:07.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,動く
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:07.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今は動くが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:09.23,default,,0,0,0,,I can move them now,\Nbut only for a while more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:12.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それもあと少し
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:12.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっううっう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:18.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっうぐぐぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:18.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まじかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:20.20,default,,0,0,0,,Is this for real?\NIt's really happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:24.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほんとのことかよこれ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:24.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:28.41,default,,0,0,0,,No! I want to be saved!\NI really want to be saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:27.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助かりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:27.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当は助かりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:35.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:36.75,default,,0,0,0,,T-That...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:38.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:38.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.63,0:07:38.39,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:51.01,default,,0,0,0,,I can't...\NNot after losing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:51.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違う
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:51.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しちゃいけないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:55.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けた上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:55.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さらに自分を
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:56.84,default,,0,0,0,,I can't afford to\Ndisgrace myself any further...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:59.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おとしめてどうする
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:59.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この男は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:08:01.34,default,,0,0,0,,This man does not forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:02.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間違っても許したりしない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:04.38,default,,0,0,0,,I already know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:05.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってるじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:09.89,default,,0,0,0,,I won't beg for my life,\NI will take it like a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:08.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なら命乞いなどするな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:14.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,耐えろ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:14.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,胸を張れ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:12.27,default,,0,0,0,,Endure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:18.13,default,,0,0,0,,Stand tall even as I endure\Nthe pain of losing my fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:18.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手痛く負けたときこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:18.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,胸を
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.95,0:08:21.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:21.13,default,,0,0,0,,K-Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:25.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やれ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:25.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:25.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:22.86,default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.90,default,,0,0,0,,But... Kaiji! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:31.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:31.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:31.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は負けたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:28.16,default,,0,0,0,,It's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:30.97,default,,0,0,0,,I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:35.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,受け入れる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:35.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けを
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:34.98,default,,0,0,0,,I will accept my defeat!\NI lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:39.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっはっは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:39.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがカイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:41.82,default,,0,0,0,,I expected nothing less from you,\NKaiji. I look up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:42.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしが見込んだ男
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:47.78,default,,0,0,0,,Normally, this would be crumpled\Nand thrown into the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:46.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本来これはこのまま握りつぶして
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:49.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゴミ箱行き
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:49.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうやってただ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:51.60,default,,0,0,0,,It would then disappear for good...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:51.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,消えていくだけのものだが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:56.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,命乞いをしないカイジ君の
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:56.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見識に敬意を表して
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:56.16,default,,0,0,0,,But as a sign of respect for\Nupholding your pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:09:00.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,特別にこれをプレゼントしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:59.56,default,,0,0,0,,I shall give it to you\Nas a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:04.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっはっは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:04.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,済んでしまえば
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:04.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,単なる紙くず
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:03.92,default,,0,0,0,,After this is over, it will be\Nnothing but a piece of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:09.68,default,,0,0,0,,But this paper is tinged with\Nthe luck of a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:07.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかしこの紙くずには王の強運が
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:11.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,染み付いておる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:11.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしその強運を
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:16.16,default,,0,0,0,,If you're able to claim this luck\Nfor your own from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:16.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君が自分のものとして
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:16.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後の人生に生かせたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:20.76,default,,0,0,0,,your life might be\None of immense wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:18.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゆくゆくは巨万の富を
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:20.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,築きあげるかもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:23.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっはっはっは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:23.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほれ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:23.06,default,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:25.39,default,,0,0,0,,More importantly,\Ntell me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:27.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことより教えてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:31.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よく考えたら俺はまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:33.23,default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,\NI have yet to know your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:35.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたの名前も聞いてねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:36.50,default,,0,0,0,,Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:38.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,教えてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:38.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ははっはっはっはっはっはっは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,0:09:40.51,default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mentioned it,\Nthat is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:41.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああそういえばそうだったな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:43.84,default,,0,0,0,,My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:52.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしの名は
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:52.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兵藤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:52.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兵藤和尊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:47.72,default,,0,0,0,,Hyodo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:52.52,default,,0,0,0,,Hyodo Kazutaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:55.52,default,,0,0,0,,Hyodo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:10:03.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兵藤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:10:03.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兵藤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:10:03.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その名前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:10:03.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:58.96,default,,0,0,0,,Hyodo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:03.46,default,,0,0,0,,I will not forget that name!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:06.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっはっはっは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:06.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:09.51,default,,0,0,0,,I will not forget\Nyour name too, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:10.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君の名は忘れんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:10.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.51,0:10:10.07,default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:14.27,default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:20.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くふう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:20.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,受け止めるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:22.16,default,,0,0,0,,I will endure... this pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:24.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:24.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この恐ろしさを
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:24.36,default,,0,0,0,,I'll accept this fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:29.15,default,,0,0,0,,I won't close my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:31.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目はつぶらない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:31.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つぶらない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:31.66,default,,0,0,0,,I won't close my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:35.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いやあああ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:44.13,default,,0,0,0,,With this, the nightmare\Ncomes to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:43.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうして悪夢の夜に終止符が
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:46.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,打たれた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:46.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの血によって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:47.11,default,,0,0,0,,It ends with Kaiji's blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.84,default,,0,0,0,,A painful dawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:58.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,苦い朝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:58.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一攫千金の夢破れ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:11:00.75,default,,0,0,0,,Where the losers are hurt and the\Ndream of 100 million is shattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:11:01.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,傷を負った敗者たちの朝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:04.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジたちは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:04.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兵藤側の用意した車が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:06.26,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji and the others are waiting for\Nthe cars prepared by Hyodo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:08.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,到着するまで待機
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:08.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けがに加え
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:12.26,default,,0,0,0,,The young men are now\Ninjured and bear heavier debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:13.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さらに大きな借金を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:13.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,背負わされる若者たち
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:15.26,default,,0,0,0,,It is tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:17.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悲惨な状況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:17.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし全ては
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:21.84,default,,0,0,0,,But these are the fruits of the\Nseeds which they have sown...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:22.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分がまいた種
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:22.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自業自得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:25.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この紙くずには王の強運が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.69,0:11:27.41,default,,0,0,0,,This paper is tinged with\Nthe luck of a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:28.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,染み付いておる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:28.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしその強運を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:33.47,default,,0,0,0,,If you're able to claim this luck\Nfor your own from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:31.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分の物として後の人生に
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:35.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生かせたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:35.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゆくゆくは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.47,0:11:37.29,default,,0,0,0,,your life might be\None of immense wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:39.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,巨万の富を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:41.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:43.76,default,,0,0,0,,He's just toying with me!\NImmense wealth?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:46.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何が巨万の富だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:46.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぬけぬけと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:48.08,default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe in such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.25,0:11:48.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなもの信じねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:51.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:49.38,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:53.50,default,,0,0,0,,It's not there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:55.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:55.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ないんすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:58.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一応イカサマの証拠に
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:58.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なっちゃうから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:12:00.22,default,,0,0,0,,We brought this with us as\Nit is proof that you cheated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:01.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持って来たんすけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:01.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ないんす
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:01.36,default,,0,0,0,,But it's not there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:05.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんが仕込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:05.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たりくじが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:05.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくら探しても
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:03.51,default,,0,0,0,,The fake lottery ticket that\Nyou put in isn't here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:05.75,default,,0,0,0,,We've already searched\Nnumerous times...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:09.48,default,,0,0,0,,How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:10.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ないわけねえだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:12.49,default,,0,0,0,,It must have fallen into the box...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:13.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負の前に黒服が振ったとき
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:16.88,default,,0,0,0,,...when that guy shuffled\Nthe lot before the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:17.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何かの拍子に中に落ちたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.37,default,,0,0,0,,It has to be that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:20.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:20.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:19.32,default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:22.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,順番にチェックして
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:22.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,抜いていったら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:22.62,default,,0,0,0,,We checked them\None by one...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:27.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうくじが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:27.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:24.73,default,,0,0,0,,It's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.23,0:12:26.19,default,,0,0,0,,See!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:27.78,default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:35.83,default,,0,0,0,,What's that in the corner?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:36.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ隅のそれ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:44.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うそ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:44.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:44.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:43.95,default,,0,0,0,,It can't be! This... can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:47.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,馬鹿な
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:46.02,default,,0,0,0,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:49.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっうう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:50.86,default,,0,0,0,,Ka-Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:53.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:53.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうことだこれ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:52.98,default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:54.28,default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:56.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:56.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決まってる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:56.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この箱に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:12:55.63,default,,0,0,0,,There's only one explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:13:00.20,default,,0,0,0,,The only hands that went into\Nthe box were Hyodo's and mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:13:01.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手を入れたのは俺と
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:13:01.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの兵藤しかいねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.35,0:13:02.97,default,,0,0,0,,He was the one who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:03.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつがやったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:04.20,default,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:07.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり１回目にくじを引くとき
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:07.21,default,,0,0,0,,When he was drawing\Nthe lot for the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:10.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつは俺が仕込んだくじを抜き
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.86,0:13:10.92,default,,0,0,0,,He must have pulled out\Nthe lot which I inserted,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:15.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,丸め
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:15.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,破棄したんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:14.45,default,,0,0,0,,taken it out and crumpled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:17.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見つからないはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:16.86,default,,0,0,0,,Of course I could not find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:18.95,default,,0,0,0,,That would mean that...\Nthe director...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:20.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ会長は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:25.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気がついていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:25.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちの戦略
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:25.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕掛けを
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:24.96,default,,0,0,0,,He figured out our strategy!\NOur setup!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:30.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ１回目に引くことも
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:30.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できたっていう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:30.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長の発言は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:30.20,default,,0,0,0,,Then... when he claimed that he was\Nable to draw it in the first try...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:32.34,default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't lying,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:36.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はったりでも何でもない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:36.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やろうと思えばできた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:36.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:34.00,default,,0,0,0,,he could have done it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:40.18,default,,0,0,0,,However, he probably wanted to\Nsee the reaction on my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:40.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おそらくやつは仕込んだくじが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:40.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見つからなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:40.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うろたえる俺の
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:42.36,default,,0,0,0,,...when I couldn't find the lot\Nwhich I placed in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,反応が見たかったんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:48.85,default,,0,0,0,,But isn't it weird that he drew\Nthe winning lot on the second try?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:45.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でもそう考えると
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:47.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か２回目に当たりを引いたのも
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:50.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怪しいっていうか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:50.02,default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:50.98,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:52.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういえば
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:52.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:52.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:52.98,default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:01.46,default,,0,0,0,,Was I blind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:04.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,節穴か
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:04.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:04.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は今まで何を
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:05.19,default,,0,0,0,,What have I been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:07.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見ていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.43,default,,0,0,0,,Here! This crease mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:11.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この折った跡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:11.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兵藤は最初に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:10.93,default,,0,0,0,,Hyodo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:13.44,default,,0,0,0,,When we were placing the lots, he\Nfolded it after I took my hand away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:14.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人で当たりくじを入れたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:18.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,箱の中でくじを離す際に折った
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:22.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くふう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:22.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:24.33,default,,0,0,0,,That was enough\Nfor him to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.74,0:14:26.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,十分だったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.74,0:14:26.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目印としては
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:28.78,default,,0,0,0,,The rest were not folded,\Nso it stood out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:28.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,他のくじは真っさらなんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:32.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:32.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:32.66,default,,0,0,0,,I know... I can tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:36.82,default,,0,0,0,,This line is so obvious when\NI feel it with my thumb...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:35.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親指の腹で折れた線をなぞると
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.32,0:14:39.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっきりと折れ目が
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.32,0:14:39.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:38.96,default,,0,0,0,,Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:40.54,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:45.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:45.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やられた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:45.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが王の強運の正体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:46.45,default,,0,0,0,,I've been tricked! The truth behind\Nthe king's luck is to leave a mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:48.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,刻印
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:48.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっはっはっは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:53.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,面白かろう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:53.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが王の道だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:50.57,default,,0,0,0,,It's interesting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.75,0:14:53.44,default,,0,0,0,,This is the king's path...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:57.33,default,,0,0,0,,The king has to win the battles\Nthat must be won...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:57.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つべくして勝つのが王の道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:15:02.42,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, a king never fights\Na losing battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:15:00.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:15:00.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王は負ける戦は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:04.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せぬものよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:04.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふっふっふっふ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.35,0:15:08.32,default,,0,0,0,,You're too naive, Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:08.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだまだ甘いのう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:08.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:14.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっはっはっはっはっは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:35.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,折ってたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:35.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも兵藤は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:32.81,default,,0,0,0,,It's been folded...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:39.94,default,,0,0,0,,But when exactly did Hyodo\Nrealise our trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:38.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつから気が付いてたんですかね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:40.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちの仕掛けに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:48.83,default,,0,0,0,,He probably confirmed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:50.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,多分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:50.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確信したのはやつが賭け金を
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:54.33,default,,0,0,0,,...when I accepted his bid to\Nraise the bet to 100 million...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:54.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１億に上げ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:54.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が受けたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:16:00.99,default,,0,0,0,,Hyodo saw the game of E-Card\Nbetween Tonegawa and me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:15:59.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兵藤は俺と利根川との
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:02.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,Ｅカードを見て
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:02.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺がここ一番で
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:05.30,default,,0,0,0,,and figured that I don't rely on\Nluck during crucial situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:06.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負を運否天賦で戦ってないこと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:09.82,default,,0,0,0,,The more important the match,\Nthe more I'll need to be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:08.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,重い勝負になればなるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:11.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝算に張る
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:11.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪く言えば
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:12.47,default,,0,0,0,,To say it bluntly,\NI'm always scheming...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:12.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,策を弄している
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.96,0:16:18.49,default,,0,0,0,,He saw through my habit and\Nused the 100 million as a bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その癖みたいなものを見抜き
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:20.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,賭け金を１億に
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:20.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,釣り上げてきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:23.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを受ければ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:23.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これはもう間違いなく俺が
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:23.20,default,,0,0,0,,If I accepted it,\Nthis would mean that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:27.57,default,,0,0,0,,...I had set a trap for him and\Nthat I had the confidence to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:26.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何かを仕掛け
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:26.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝算を持っている
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:30.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう踏んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:30.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,となれば
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:34.51,default,,0,0,0,,There are only 2 ways to ensure\Na win in the lottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:32.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この手のくじの必勝法は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:35.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大きく分けて２種類しかない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:37.01,default,,0,0,0,,Either you rig the box,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:39.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,箱に仕掛けを打つか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:39.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,抜いたふりをして実は抜かず
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:39.38,default,,0,0,0,,or you try to pick a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.38,0:16:43.58,default,,0,0,0,,that's not inside the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:44.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別のどこかから当たりくじを
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:44.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持ってくるという
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:44.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すり替え
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:47.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから勝負前に兵藤が
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:47.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たりくじは２人で入れようと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:48.82,default,,0,0,0,,That is why Hyodo wanted\Nto put in the lots together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:50.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言い出したのは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:50.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのくじに折り目という
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:52.97,default,,0,0,0,,It was not just to fold the ticket,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:53.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目印を付けるってこともあったが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.52,0:16:58.60,default,,0,0,0,,but also to make sure that\Nit was in the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:55.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１つ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:55.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かにくじが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:17:00.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,箱に入ったという事実が
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:17:00.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,欲しかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:17:00.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入りさえすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:04.33,default,,0,0,0,,As long as it was in the box,\Nit wouldn't matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:04.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮に俺がどこかから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:04.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たりクジをでっちあげてきても
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:07.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,箱を改めれば
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:07.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１枚当たりくじが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:11.57,default,,0,0,0,,...even if I were to put in a fake\Nticket from somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:12.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出てきてしまうんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:12.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その手のインチキは通じない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:15.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残った細工は箱しかない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:15.11,default,,0,0,0,,The only thing left\Nwas the box itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:18.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして箱のどこかに当たりくじを
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:18.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕込むとしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:18.21,default,,0,0,0,,If I were to insert the ticket\Ninto the box,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:20.55,default,,0,0,0,,it had to be either\Nat the bottom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:25.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,未開封のティッシュ箱なら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:25.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これはもう底か横しかない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:24.25,default,,0,0,0,,Or... at the sides!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:28.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:28.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:28.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:33.96,default,,0,0,0,,To think that he was planning\Nthese while smiling like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:31.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:31.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へらへら笑いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:34.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兵藤ってそんなことまで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:38.55,default,,0,0,0,,No wonder we weren't\Na match for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:39.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こりゃかなわないや
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:39.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手が悪すぎた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:39.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,話が分かれば
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:41.43,default,,0,0,0,,The clearer the picture\Nbecomes,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:47.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かるほど負けるべくして
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:47.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けた感じになる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:47.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,格上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:44.00,default,,0,0,0,,the more it seems that\Nwe should have lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.82,0:17:48.41,default,,0,0,0,,His skills are in a totally\Ndifferent league!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:50.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,巨大すぎた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:50.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あまりに相手が
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:50.79,default,,0,0,0,,He was too good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.15,default,,0,0,0,,I was so foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:57.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,馬鹿だった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:17:59.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考えてみりゃそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:59.13,default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:03.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今更遅いけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:03.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,調子に乗りすぎた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:02.16,default,,0,0,0,,It's too late for that now.\NWe were overconfident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:08.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川に勝ったところで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:08.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめるべきだった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:08.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめておけば
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:06.11,default,,0,0,0,,We should have called it quits\Nwhen we defeated Tonegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:11.08,default,,0,0,0,,If we did, we would have\Nwalked away with 20 million...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:11.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,2000
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:11.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,万を得て
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:11.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悠々生還
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:15.50,default,,0,0,0,,Instead, we charged right in\Nwithout knowing our limits...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:20.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに限度を知らずに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:20.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,突っ込むから結局
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:20.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この悲惨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:19.14,default,,0,0,0,,It resulted in this disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:23.14,default,,0,0,0,,The ear aside... we don't know if\Nhis fingers can be reattached...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:23.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,耳はともかく指はくっつかどうか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:28.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮についてもまともに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:28.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,動くかどうか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:28.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.80,0:18:26.88,default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's possible, can they\Nmove the way they could before?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:31.00,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, you realised that\Na little too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:33.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あまりに気づくのが遅すぎたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:33.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今更どうにも
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:32.92,default,,0,0,0,,Nothing can be done now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:34.22,default,,0,0,0,,could have won...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:38.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:38.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は勝てた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:39.09,default,,0,0,0,,I could have won...\NI could've won the match!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:40.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てる勝負だった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:45.24,default,,0,0,0,,Hyodo had given me a chance!\NWhy didn't I exploit it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:42.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兵藤には隙があった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:45.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜそこを突けなかったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:47.63,default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a minute...\Nwhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:48.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:48.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隙って一体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:51.49,default,,0,0,0,,Hyodo left a mark\Non the winning lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:51.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兵藤はくじに印を付けてたんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:55.38,default,,0,0,0,,In other words, he was able to\Ndraw the lot in the first draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:55.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てことは当然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:55.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１回目に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:55.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引くこともできた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:58.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかしあえてそれをしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:19:00.11,default,,0,0,0,,But he didn't do that. He gave\Nme a chance to draw the lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:19:01.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一度俺に引く権利を与えた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:05.12,default,,0,0,0,,That was the opportunity\Nthat I had been given!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:03.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが隙でなくてなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:07.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明らかな緩み
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:07.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからあのとき
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:09.36,default,,0,0,0,,If only I had been\Nthinking clearly then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:10.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっとよく考えれば良かった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:13.06,default,,0,0,0,,When I couldn't find\Nthe winning lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:13.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕込んだくじが見つからないとき
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:17.41,default,,0,0,0,,why didn't I realise that\NHyodo had got rid of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:16.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜそれを兵藤が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:16.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,始末した可能性を
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.27,0:19:19.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考えなかったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:24.04,default,,0,0,0,,If I'd thought about it, I could\Nhave found the crumpled ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:22.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこに考えが至れば
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:22.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,丸められたくじを見つけることが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.67,0:19:26.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できたかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.67,0:19:26.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さらに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:25.60,default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:30.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人でくじを入れようと言った
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:30.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兵藤の言動から
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:31.11,default,,0,0,0,,I'd have figured out why Hyodo wanted\Nto put in the winning lot together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:33.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,折り目という
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:33.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兵藤が付けた当たりの刻印に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:36.11,default,,0,0,0,,I might have realised that\NHyodo had marked the ticket...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:36.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考えが届いたかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:39.59,default,,0,0,0,,In that case,\NI could have won!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:39.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなれば俺の勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:47.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ちだったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.67,0:19:46.17,default,,0,0,0,,I could have won!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:51.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:51.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:51.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのとき俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:48.84,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:51.46,default,,0,0,0,,But at that time, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:59.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神よ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:19:58.44,default,,0,0,0,,Please, god...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:20:02.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うふ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:20:02.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うふっふっふ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:05.08,default,,0,0,0,,Please give me luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:07.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神よ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:07.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺を祝福しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:07.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救え
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:09.08,default,,0,0,0,,Save me! Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:11.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:11.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐうう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:18.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あろうことか祈ってしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:17.78,default,,0,0,0,,All I did was pray during\Nthat period.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:24.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何も考えずに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:24.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神頼み
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:20.58,default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't thinking\Nabout anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:23.59,default,,0,0,0,,I relied on god...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:27.90,default,,0,0,0,,"Save me"...\N"Please help me"...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:28.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:28.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺を助けてくれだと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:31.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう自分以外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:31.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼るものなどないと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.10,default,,0,0,0,,Even though I knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:33.84,default,,0,0,0,,...the only one who could\Nsave me, was myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:34.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,骨身に染みて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:37.80,default,,0,0,0,,I should have known, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:37.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知っていたはずなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:37.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.91,0:20:41.12,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:45.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:52.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兵藤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:52.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兵藤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.70,default,,0,0,0,,Hyodo... Hyodo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:56.29,default,,0,0,0,,Hyodo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.20,0:20:59.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兵藤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.20,0:20:59.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,這わせてやるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.20,0:20:59.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつの日か
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:59.85,default,,0,0,0,,I will get my revenge one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:05.07,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji has survived\Nthe castle of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:06.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:06.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶望の城からの生還
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:09.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狂気の夜に打たれた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:11.24,default,,0,0,0,,The disappointing end to the night\Nof madness has finally ended!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:12.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,報われぬ終止符
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:18.08,default,,0,0,0,,Just you remember!\NNext time, I will be the winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:18.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚えてろ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:18.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次は俺が勝つ
